<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.4.6">
<l>cuḻaṉṟilaṅku veṅkatirōṉ tērōṭum pōymaṟaintāṉ</l>
<l>aḻaṉṟu koṭitāki yañcuṭarōṉ tāṉaṭumāl</l>
<l>ceḻuntaṭampūñ cōlaicūḻ pullāṇi kaitoḻutēṉ</l>
<l>iḻantiruntē ṉeṉṟa ṉeḻilniṟamuñ caṅkumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one with shining hot rays, slipping [away], vanished,</l>
<l rend="indent">leaving with his chariot;</l>
<l>The one with beautiful beams, becoming cruel, burning,</l>
<l rend="indent">will surely destroy me.</l>
<l>I, who worship, hands [joined], in Pullāṇi encircled by verdant ponds</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] flowering groves,</l>
<l>Have lost my lovely complexion and bangles.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
